Most important product decision reflected in this structure

This structure is built as a multi-tenant product, not a one-company internal tool.

That is why it includes:

workspaces
configurable service templates
configurable milestones
configurable lead scoring
branded admin settings
branded client portal capability
reusable proposal engine
reusable workflow package
